Hello Dear,

Hello Dear,
I saw your profile today in this site (en.pan.netcom) and i stopped to take a
very good look at it.
I want you to know that i will be intrested to know you better because you
sounded very sweet in your profile and i will like us to become friends and
know eachother the more.
Here is my email address (adabata22@yahoo.com.ph)  send me an email today
please!
Yours forever,
angela.
(Remember that distance,age or colour does not matter in a real relationship
but love matters alot).
I am waiting for your reply now!
